{"tid":2110623,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"開唔到機，求救！","createTime":"2020-07-16T05:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T15:45:38.000Z","uid":40787,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d779cfcf60325d5e7e43093124feb90e9b80080a","tid":2110623,"uid":40787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:00:00.000Z","msg":"AMD Ryzen&trade; 3 3300X<br />\n<br />\nGigabyte B450M AORUS ELITE Micro-ATX<br />\n<br />\nADATA XPG GAMMIX D10 (1 x 8GB) DDR4 3200 Mhz C16<br />\n<br />\nKingston A2000 500GB PCIe Gen3x4 M.2 2280<br />\n<br />\n Gigabyte GeForce&reg; GTX 1660 SUPER&trade; GAMING OC 6GB GDDR6<br />\n<br />\n電腦安裝windows 10後不定時會自動重新開機。。。<br />\n<br />\n有時重新開機後就再開唔到電腦，會不斷reboot..藍畫面<br />\n<br />\n用手指重裝windows嘅時候都會藍畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新機落地一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一開始就係咁... <br />\n<br />\n問題係有時部電腦一兩日內會無乜事，玩大作都load得好順，之後突然就會死機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc336e9b2f3b9bab69668ac1fd87a6955250232","tid":2110623,"uid":117037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:04:06.000Z","msg":"邊到買"},{"pid":"71be6d5f8be42f84e19bedb3324f1e3478cd9979","tid":2110623,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:20:54.000Z","msg":"藍畫面有個code，影低睇睇"},{"pid":"64d95c21387b41e7a542ed6f2b50adc6b8b49dcb","tid":2110623,"uid":225192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:48:42.000Z","msg":"試左所有野拆一拆要裝落去<br />\n可能有野鬆左接觸不良"},{"pid":"d172f786f12b537b8cb79af096665ffca873a533","tid":2110623,"uid":40787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71be6d5f8be42f84e19bedb3324f1e3478cd9979","tid":2110623,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:20:54.000Z","msg":"藍畫面有個code，影低睇睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T06:00:49.000Z","msg":"0xc0000021a &amp; 0xc000007b"},{"pid":"8c2a3239adc4